GET request to /api/files/ returns a list of files
GET request to /api/file/1 returns the file with ID 1
POST request to /api/file/ with a file object as JSON creates a new file
PUT request to /api/file/3 with a file object as JSON updates the file with ID 3
DELETE request to /api/file/4 deletes the file with ID 4
DELETE request to /api/files/ deletes all the users